data.name: Definitionservice1
data.value:
The platform aims to collect an integrated information base that includes all companies working in the field of information technology and emerging technologies, both local and international in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia, to create a reference guide for workers in the field and to enhance the role of transparency by providing correct and updated information on these companies by registering companies on the platform and obtaining Authority accreditation

Benefits of the platform for registered companies:

  • Issuing a certificate of registration of information notarized by the authority using the barcode, and it can be verified through the authority’s website.
  • Providing easy access to companies and searching for them through the Authority’s portal according to classification, services or products.
  • Providing easy communication between private and government service seekers with registered companies
